# Apple/App Store Connect private keys — never commit these
*.p8

# Firebase service account keys (Admin SDK) — never commit these. Note
# google-services.json / GoogleService-Info.plist are NOT secret (client
# identifiers only) and are intentionally tracked inside android/app/ and
# ios/App/App/ — this only blocks stray copies elsewhere plus the real key.
/google-services.json
*firebase-adminsdk*.json
